sentences.english: In 1960 Khruschev headed a delegation to visit Indonesia and was royally treated by his host.
sentences.chinese: 率團出訪印度尼西亞，他受到了主人的盛情款待。

sentences.english: Silat is a unique martial art originating from the archipelago. The most popular sports in Indonesia are soccer and badminton.
sentences.chinese: 印度尼西亞最受歡迎的體育項目是足球和羽毛球。

sentences.english: In the end of 1956, Outside Islands Rebellion broke.
sentences.chinese: 1956年末，印度尼西亞爆發外島叛亂。

sentences.english: Indonesia's rupiah trillionaires have so much money that it's difficult to count it.
sentences.chinese: 印度尼西亞的億萬富豪錢多得都沒法準確計算了。

sentences.english: Of the 67 cases confirmed to date in Indonesia, 51 have been fatal.
sentences.chinese: 在印度尼西亞迄今確診的76例中，有51例死亡。

sentences.english: Indonesia is a member of the G-20.
sentences.chinese: 印度尼西亞是20國集團的成員國。

sentences.english: The newly confirmed case brings the total in Indonesia to 29.
sentences.chinese: 新確認的病例使印度尼西亞的病例總數達到29例。

sentences.english: Susilo, President of Indonesia, attended the opening ceremony.
sentences.chinese: 印度尼西亞總統蘇希洛出席會議開幕式。

sentences.english: Indonesias Health Ministry says a 17-year old woman has died of bird flu.
sentences.chinese: 印度尼西亞衛生部說，一名17歲的婦女死於禽流感。

sentences.english: The newly confirmed case brings the total number in Indonesia to 12.
sentences.chinese: 該新確認的病例使印度尼西亞病例總數增至12例。

sentences.english: That was Mount Tambora, on the island of Sumbawa in Indonesia.
sentences.chinese: 發生在印度尼西亞坦松巴哇島上的坦博拉火山上。

sentences.english: Within Indonesia, the situation is most critical in Riau.
sentences.chinese: 在印度尼西亞國內，情況最嚴重的地區就是廖內省。

sentences.english: Indonesia was worst affected with as many as 219,000 people killed.
sentences.chinese: 受災害性影響最大的印度尼西亞有21萬9千人喪生。

sentences.english: The Indonesia virus strain may be very important one day.
sentences.chinese: 有一天印度尼西亞病毒株可能極其重要。
鳥瞰維米，爪哇，印度尼西亞，1994。

sentences.english: It gives me great pleasure to visit Indonesia, the beautiful country of thousand islands.
sentences.chinese: 我很高興來到美麗的千島之國印度尼西亞訪問。
